Package ui.labels

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardView
    This JLabel is a view for card model It containing the original card object and an image based on its type This view will changed its border color based on the number it has been clicked
    CountryObsLabel
    Country label representing countries in the game play Implements Observer in the observer pattern, Observes Country objects Updates the value of armies in the Country and the owner's Color
    InfoObsLabel  
    OutcomeObsLabel
    Outcome text representing outcome of player commands in the game play Implements Observer in the observer pattern, Observes game outcome in the GamePlay object Updates the String text to be shown in the UI
    PlayerTurnObsLabel
    Player turn label representing the current player's turn during gameplay Implements Observer in the observer pattern, Observes current player in the game play Updates the Color of the current player to be shown by the label in UI
